title: American Horror Story, 9-1-1, ACS Versace Friday News Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I whould love Americain horror story on Netflix

I think you will enjoy the Versace ACS so far.  I have been watching every week.  Episode 6 will return in 2 weeks.  Idk why it is taking a week off.  The first 5 episodes are great, though they do not follow the conventional linear timeline, so beware!  Major time jumps around back and fourth with the murders.  The acting is very stellar 👍

btw Mary. I know it's a while away. but I definitely hope you review the new Halloween movie coming out October 19th. Idk if your a Michael Myers fan or not but would definitely love to hear your input.
The only thing I've watched from TNT was a tiny bit of Rizzoli & Isles lmao
description:
Host is MaryGirl Moody. Updates on American Horror Story Season 8, Ryan Murphy and his $300 million dollar deal with Netflix, and Lily Rabe's new show. Let's talk 9-1-1 and American Crime Story Versace.
